193
00:17:51,161 --> 00:17:52,361
Can we talk?

194
00:17:52,961 --> 00:17:55,281
- Right now?
- Yes, but not here.

195
00:18:02,841 --> 00:18:05,081
Sorry about earlier.
You angry?

196
00:18:05,201 --> 00:18:06,241
No.

197
00:18:06,921 --> 00:18:08,161
