Is it about Lionel?

205
00:18:38,401 --> 00:18:39,401
No, it's not.

206
00:18:39,881 --> 00:18:41,161
So explain.

207
00:18:43,601 --> 00:18:45,201
I don't know you, Sami.

208
00:18:46,201 --> 00:18:47,281
5 years now.

209
00:18:47,401 --> 00:18:50,241
