or what I like.

210
00:18:50,361 --> 00:18:52,601
You don't like my friends.

211
00:18:52,801 --> 00:18:55,841
We choose to do different things,
don't we?

212
00:18:56,241 --> 00:18:57,881
Yes. But I've had enough.

213
00:18:58,001 --> 00:18:59,921
